original_raw:
example (h : ¬ (P ∨ Q)) : ¬ P ∧ ¬ Q  := by
  constructor
  intro p
  have duh : P∨ Q := by
    left
    exact p
  exact h duh
  intro q
  have duh : P∨ Q := by
    right
    exact q
  exact h duh
new_raw_BASIC:
example (h : ¬ (P ∨ Q)) : ¬ P ∧ ¬ Q := by
  constructor
  case left: ¬P
    intro p
    exact h (Or.inl p)
  case right: ¬Q
    intro q
    exact h (Or.inr q)
